# WORD FORGE

## Screen Flow

The game should feel like opening an old government language training file.

Everything is clean.

No floating particles.

No unnecessary animations.

No clutter.

Every screen looks like an official language training document stored inside an old archive.

The visual style should use:

* Dark walnut wood
* Aged paper
* Black ink
* Brass and gold accents
* Olive-green buttons

