# SCREEN 3

# Academies

The screen resembles an old filing cabinet.

Every Academy appears as a vintage paper folder.

Example

```text
📁 Synonyms

58% Complete
```

```text
📁 Antonyms

12% Complete
```

```text
📁 Rhyming Words

0% Complete
```

All Academies are available from the beginning.

None are locked.

Completed Academies receive a gold **MASTERED** stamp.

Each folder displays:

* Academy Name
* Completion Percentage
* Mastered Stamp (if completed)

Selecting a folder opens that Academy.

